Well heres a bigger map of this map. I said that I would make a bigger one so I did, the new map features the following:

- HDR - 36 spawns - a single nade - 2 pistols - 4 smgs - 4 shotguns - 4 machineguns - 12 rifels - 12 snipers - and two buyzones

Well i don't bother doing the credits, but you already know it...

Asses if you like it, don't if you got a good reason. Hope you like it... Enjoy!

A little information about the screenshots: I took them with my textures on low, I didn't notice and didn't bothered to remake them, I will maybe update it later on... I fixed the thing with the lights. Just if anyone noticed.
